## if the conversation stack is empty, and there is an unresolved tie, and it is in the topstate, prompt instructor for more information, or further action. Unless there is a relevant operator is proposed on the topstate, the agent is not pursuing any intention/goal. intention ^category none

sp {propose*change-in-conversation-state-scenario1
   (state <s> ^task <t>
   	      ^conversation-stack <cs>)
   (<cs> ^segment none)
   (<t> ^category none
   	^progress <tp>)
   (<tp> ^status.type unresolved-tie)
-->
   (<s> ^operator <op> + >)
   (<op> ^name push-segment-stack
   	 ^initiator agent
	 ^purpose-type get-further-instruction) 
}
